{"tid":1700664,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日會出席港大社科頒獎典禮嘅可唔可以陪我戴口罩","createTime":"2019-11-08T15:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T00:44:55.000Z","uid":92806,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4bcb5a56d7d05d15a4265a37cb04073a878fc9e8","tid":1700664,"uid":92806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"我哋用咗咁長時間去搵我哋嘅校長，佢背棄學子，連十一月嘅所謂直接對話都唔知要等到幾時。鄰校嘅周同學今晨不治，22歲讀UST打netball 嘅佢，理應喺台上同同學笑住上台，理應喺球場上發光發熱，理應拖住女朋友嘅手喺大學遊走，理應喺屋企飲住父母煲嘅湯。佢所經歷緊嘅人生，理應都同我哋一樣。有良知嘅人都清楚知道，唔係佢摔低導致由三樓平台墜下，而係個政權將佢推下去。<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可以放過任何可以向學校施壓嘅機會，作為社科生，我哋更加以爭取社會公義為己任，所以我好懇請聽日會去student prize presentation ceremony嘅大家，陪我戴上口罩或面具。<br />\n<br />\nThe dead cannot cry out for justice. It is a duty of the living to do so for them."},{"pid":"210bc402249a54ee6209f39e9b828cba1f40a270","tid":1700664,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">幫手入黎Rt + like + reply</span><br />\n【英美戰線】我淨係知，唔可以輸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700470</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"58dffdd55463766bb0e4cc9cfb76f1b3ae791620","tid":1700664,"uid":105833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:36:21.000Z","msg":"鄰校幫推"},{"pid":"2a110b36f16a9308c3ae4b793ee76f10f1199612","tid":1700664,"uid":29929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"張翔就升撚數啦 唉"},{"pid":"3960fd189a76d44b05c43fb520c673d7d11673a3","tid":1700664,"uid":1103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:37:30.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"42faf785bedb0c508c3d617ff01184fd38895987","tid":1700664,"uid":1103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:37:40.000Z","msg":"shared"},{"pid":"ded6620098e1d17cf23fbdb7a8008ddc37be47eb","tid":1700664,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:38:43.000Z"